* store the array at 1000 and the program at 3000
X           EQU     1000
            ORIG    3000

MAXIMUM     STJ     EXIT
INIT        ENT3    0,1
            JMP     CHANGEM
LOOP        CMPA    X,3
            JGE     *+3
* store the new max in A and the index in I2
CHANGEM     ENT2    0,3
            LDA     X,3
            DEC3    1
            J3P     LOOP
EXIT        HLT
